  in 1995 , blackmun received the u.s. senator john heinz award for greatest public service by an elected or appointed official , an award given out annually by jefferson awards.http://www.jeffersonawards.org/pastwinners/national   in 1997 , blackmun portrayed justice joseph story in the steven spielberg film amistad , making him the only supreme court justice to have played a judge in a motion picture .

the love boat : harry blackmun played joseph story , supreme court justice from 1811 to 1845 , in this film about a spanish boat

